DAY 4
I learned the first half of chapter 8-----Function!
今天学了第八章的前一半

I learned how to define functions (parameters and arguments) and how to pass arguments (location, keyword, default value)
我学会了如何定义函数（形参和实参），以及如何传递实参（位置，关键字，默认值）

Then, I began to learn the concept of return value. Functions can not only output directly, but also process data and return a certain value
接着，我开始学习返回值这个概念，函数不光能直接输出，还可以对数据进行处理，并返回一定的值

---Exempel---
def get_formatted_name(first_name, last_name):
    """返回全名"""
    full_name = first_name + ' ' + last_name
    return full_name.title()
musician = get_formatted_name('John', 'Smith')
print(musician)

---Q---
def get_formatted_name(first_name, last_name):
    """返回全名"""
    full_name = first_name + ' ' + last_name
    print(full_name.title())
get_formatted_name('John', 'Smith')

You can get the same result by writing this way. What is the use of return?
这样写可以得到相同的结果，那么return有什么用呢？

Then I learned how to make the argument optional
接着，我学习了如何让arugment变成可选的

并且在案例中学到了，Python对于非空字符串的判断是True,None 可以理解为占位符
And I learned from the case that Python's judgment on non empty strings is true，None can be understood as a placeholder

