I have encountered great difficulties in learning to transmit lists to functions. 
There are always various problems that cause my program to fail to run normally.
Sometimes I know what the problem is, sometimes I don 't.
我在学习向函数转递列表时遭遇了较大的困难，
总是会有各种各样的问题导致我的程序无法正常运行。
有时候我知道问题出在哪里，有时候则不知道。

I only learned a little bit after going through it like this. 
You know, I learned from 12:00 at noon to 9:00 at night, and I took a break for twoorthree hours.
这样子捋一遍下来居然只学了这么一点内容。
要知道我可是从中午12点差不多学到晚上9点，中间就休息了两三个小时。
